name: YooshiApe
description: Meet Yooshi Ape! It's a meme token on Binance Smart Chain. Made by help of friends and fans. Yooshi Ape's mission is simple yet electrifying: harness the Yooshi craze to bring profit and excitement to meme enthusiasts. Its mission is to amplify Yooshi Ape, highlighting its distinct character, and create rewarding opportunities for meme enthusiasts. Join on this exhilarating adventure, where memes turn into profits, and the original Yooshi shines brighter than ever before! Yooshi Ape's main goal is to support Angel Syndrome children. Join our unique journey where memes meet profit, and together, we make a difference. Our mission is to promote Yooshi, raise awareness of its altruistic goals, and create profit opportunities for meme enthusiasts while supporting Yooshi's original purpose.
